# Component Library

Local MDSvX component guidance for Shitrat Cli.

pi-notes ships standard components and auto-imports project-local Svelte components from `.brain/components/**/*.svelte` when they are used in `.svx` pages.

## Rules

- Keep `.svx` as the narrative shell.
- Put large structured data in `.brain/data/**`.
- Put reusable renderers in `.brain/components/**`.
- Prefer focused components over boolean prop soup.
- Show provenance, freshness, privacy, and action side effects when a component reads data or triggers work.

## Useful standard components

- `<NoteCallout tone="info" title="Note">...</NoteCallout>`
- `<StatusPill label="active" tone="success" />`
- `<SourceReference path="src/file.ts" label="Source" />`
- `<ReviewReceipt batchId="..." status="handled" />`
- `<DiagramFrame src="/diagrams/example.svg" source="docs/diagrams/example" renderer="mermaid" />`

## Project components

Create project-specific components in `.brain/components/` only when a shape repeats or depends on structured data.
